Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.93,0:00:06.80,Narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,Once upon a time, there was a maiden in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.60,0:00:14.98,Narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,"I want to tell my beloved how I feel, but my\Nlove might be over the moment I say it."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.98,0:00:19.05,Narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,Every day she suffered, agonizing in this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.05,0:00:23.22,Narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,She took no meals, and she was unable even to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.22,0:00:28.85,Narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,And finally, she died without ever having\Nbeen able to communicate her feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.29,0:00:38.70,Narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,But the man she loved married another woman and lived happily\Never after, without ever even knowing the maiden had existed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.58,0:02:30.67,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Quack?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.18,0:02:34.22,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I fell asleep while I was still a duck.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.22,0:02:36.05,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,In Fakir's arms...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.32,0:02:39.72,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Fakir bandaged this for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.32,0:02:43.45,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Quack!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.19,0:02:47.49,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Quack...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.83,0:02:49.13,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Quack?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.13,0:02:50.37,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,They're stopped?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.37,0:02:52.83,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations, Little Duck.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.67,0:02:54.37,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Quack.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.37,0:02:57.93,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,The prince's pride has returned to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.07,0:03:00.11,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oof...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.11,0:03:02.71,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Qua-qua-qua-qua-quack!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.71,0:03:07.25,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Now all the shards of the prince's\Nheart have returned to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.25,0:03:08.52,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.52,0:03:11.15,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,So right now, he's...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.15,0:03:15.82,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, he must be suffering right about now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.82,0:03:16.69,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.69,0:03:20.66,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Because he doesn't have ALL of the heart shards yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.66,0:03:23.50,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What? But you just said they'd all returned...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.97,0:03:25.47,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Drosselmeyer-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.47,0:03:29.87,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,The shards that were hidden inside chinks in other\Npeople's hearts have all been returned now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.87,0:03:33.04,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,But those aren't ALL the shards.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.04,0:03:34.54,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.54,0:03:38.41,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course. His heart has to keep the\Nraven from moving, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.41,0:03:40.72,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,That IS why it was shattered.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.72,0:03:41.75,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.85,0:03:42.88,Person2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, dear, I don't have time for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.28,0:03:43.45,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.45,0:03:46.99,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what should I do?! Where's the rest of his heart?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.99,0:03:49.26,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,The prince's heart is being dyed in raven's blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.26,0:03:50.86,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I put it back to normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.86,0:03:51.86,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.86,0:03:57.70,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bye, Little Duck! We'll have the opportunity\Nto meet again...when I feel like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.10,0:04:04.37,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Did she disappear zura?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.41,0:04:11.18,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You say you met Drosselmeyer?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.41,0:04:15.92,Notes,,0000,0000,0000,,"A Midsummer Night's Dream"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.18,0:04:16.25,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. It looks like when I meet Drosselmeyer-san, time stops.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.25,0:04:17.98,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,You can come in now, Fakir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.39,0:04:20.12,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened then?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.12,0:04:23.73,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,He said the rest of the heart shards\Nwere sealing away the raven.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.73,0:04:29.19,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,And... that the heart shards I returned\Nto Mytho are hurting him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.13,0:04:31.53,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.53,0:04:32.20,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.20,0:04:38.27,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,If Drosselmeyer is right, the moment the rest of the heart shards\Nare returned will be the moment of the raven's resurrection.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.27,0:04:40.50,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, the moment when the fight begins.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.04,0:04:44.31,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Mytho has to be prepared for some suffering already.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.31,0:04:48.95,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,If you aren't prepared to handle that too,\Nyou should stop being Princess Tutu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.45,0:04:51.09,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll protect Mytho with my sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.09,0:04:54.76,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I don't really want you brandishing a sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.76,0:04:56.29,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, it's dangerous and stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.29,0:04:59.23,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,So you don't acknowledge me as a knight?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.23,0:05:00.16,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.16,0:05:02.00,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, you've been doing research\Nin books and stuff all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.00,0:05:06.59,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,So I just think you could be a knight like that instead of...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.67,0:05:08.87,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Fakir...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.87,0:05:10.97,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,If your wounds have healed, then go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.97,0:05:11.94,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll walk you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.14,0:05:16.44,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.95,0:05:18.88,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not particularly mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.41,0:05:20.75,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,You ARE mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.05,0:05:27.45,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thank you for bandaging me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.02,0:05:29.01,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.36,0:05:30.55,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Good night!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.09,0:05:34.00,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,A knight who can't even protect a princess, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.00,0:05:37.97,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What can you do? A knight who couldn't even die.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.97,0:05:41.60,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,In the story, you're no longer needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.60,0:05:46.54,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Will the story stay exactly the same whether I'm here or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.94,0:05:53.21,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Fakir was acting strange, getting mad and\Nthen suddenly getting depressed...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.58,0:05:56.72,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahiru-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.72,0:05:57.85,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.85,0:06:00.59,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,You were mere centimeters from marrying Cat-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.59,0:06:01.99,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.99,0:06:04.63,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,You were all spaced out. Thinking about Fakir-sama, I'll bet!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.63,0:06:05.68,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.96,0:06:08.33,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to tell him how you feel, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.33,0:06:09.26,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.47,0:06:12.53,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, why don't you try sending him a love letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.63,0:06:12.53,Person2,,0000,0000,0000,,What? No, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.60,0:06:14.73,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll do it, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.70,0:06:19.91,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought this might happen, so I prepared\Na love letter to Fakir-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.91,0:06:20.61,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.61,0:06:26.05,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,If you wander around school holding that,\NBottom-san will come, so ask her to pass it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.05,0:06:27.45,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Bottom-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.45,0:06:29.68,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,She delivers love letters for people.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.68,0:06:32.32,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Word is she knows the feelings of people in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.32,0:06:34.09,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,She knows their feelings?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.09,0:06:37.49,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll call it "The Great Lovey-Dovey Letter Operation"!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.66,0:06:40.10,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,So good luck, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.10,0:06:43.00,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, we have to prepare to comfort her later!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.47,0:06:45.40,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,A love letter to Fakir...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.40,0:06:50.54,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,If I gave him something like this, he'd say, "Don't waste\Ntime doing stupid stuff, idiot," or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.17,0:06:54.38,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that lovey-dovey zura?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.38,0:06:56.64,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,But she "knows feelings"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.64,0:07:02.11,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if I'd know how Mytho really\Nfeels, if I had that kind of power...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.02,0:07:04.28,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Bottom-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.65,0:07:09.62,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Prince? Prince, aren't you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.26,0:07:13.63,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this? It looks like he fought with someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.47,0:07:23.37,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be... that something is happening because\Na new heart shard returned to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.38,0:07:36.67,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to overcome the raven's blood, if I'm a proud prince...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.02,0:07:40.45,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what kind of person Bottom-san is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.90,0:07:49.26,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you agonizing over your love?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.26,0:07:51.07,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you Bottom...san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.07,0:07:52.47,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,A donkey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.47,0:07:55.64,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Bottom, friend of all those who are in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.64,0:07:56.97,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,So, where's your letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.97,0:07:58.17,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.17,0:08:00.31,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's... not a tail zura.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.31,0:08:01.84,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's your tail zura?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.84,0:08:02.57,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.34,0:08:04.71,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Bottom-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.65,0:08:07.91,Notes,,0000,0000,0000,,Donkey-lonkey, lovey-dovey, donkey...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.28,0:08:11.12,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Bottom-san! Bottom-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.52,0:08:16.92,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Bottom-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.49,0:08:19.89,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got it all wrong! I'm definitely not Bottom!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.89,0:08:21.73,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got nothing to do with letters!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.20,0:08:24.72,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you that upperclassman...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.47,0:08:26.59,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,You found me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.60,0:08:29.13,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Hermia.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.57,0:08:33.07,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell anyone, okay? I'll be sure to deliver this letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.07,0:08:40.22,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, that's okay! My friend wrote it for me, but she's\Ngot the wrong idea about which person I like...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.22,0:08:40.85,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.85,0:08:42.95,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm Duck!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.95,0:08:47.81,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahiru-san, huh? Well, then, when you've written\Nyour real letter, bring it to me any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.19,0:08:53.56,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't confess my love. There are some\Ncircumstances that prevent it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.10,0:08:55.16,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.16,0:08:59.00,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Hermia-san, do you know people's feelings?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.00,0:08:59.73,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.73,0:09:03.14,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Well, I wouldn't say I know them;\Nit's more like sometimes I sense them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.47,0:09:09.48,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Like, "Ah, this person is in love," or "She looks\Nlonely; maybe she has a broken heart."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.48,0:09:10.78,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.78,0:09:12.97,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm tall, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.38,0:09:16.82,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm always the one furthest to the back of the corps.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.82,0:09:22.35,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,But one day, I noticed that I could see the feeling\Nof being in love on everyone's backs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.26,0:09:26.32,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,The heartrending feelings of people in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.13,0:09:31.73,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Love is a wonderful thing, but it also makes\Npeople suffer and be sad, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.73,0:09:38.24,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,So everyone has a hard time saying "I love you,"\Nand they're all keeping their feelings inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.24,0:09:42.71,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd at least like to help those people.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.71,0:09:44.45,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.45,0:09:48.52,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,But you know, lately it's all letters to Mytho-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.52,0:09:49.92,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,To Mytho?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.92,0:09:57.53,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I deliver lots of letters to him every day, but most are\Nfrom people whose feelings won't be returned...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.53,0:10:01.36,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you see Mytho every day, Hermia-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.36,0:10:05.23,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Well, actually, Mytho-sama comes to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.23,0:10:08.04,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,So then, do you know something about Mytho's feelings?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.04,0:10:08.60,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.60,0:10:10.07,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything is fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.07,0:10:14.68,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. Mytho-sama's feelings alone I just can't figure out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.68,0:10:16.01,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.71,0:10:19.95,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, do you like Mytho-sama too, by any chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.95,0:10:20.72,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.72,0:10:23.75,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, do you like him too, Hermia-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.75,0:10:27.62,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? No, you've got it all wrong! I don't\Nhave any feelings for Mytho-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.62,0:10:29.85,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I have someone I like named Lysander!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.09,0:10:32.82,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Lysander-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.61,0:10:47.56,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to get more heart shards back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.25,0:10:52.51,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Kraehe...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.99,0:11:07.53,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Who does the prince's heart belong to?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.53,0:11:09.90,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is the prince's heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.90,0:11:11.83,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.46,0:11:45.66,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Prince, you don't have to suffer anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.20,0:11:50.23,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Your princess is me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.74,0:11:53.61,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll save you from your suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.95,0:12:02.94,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Return, prince of the crows. Return to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.95,0:12:09.15,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't become the prince of the crows!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.99,0:12:13.83,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,If you resist, your suffering will only continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.83,0:12:15.76,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,The suffering is nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.53,0:12:22.24,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,You have raven's blood running through\Nyour veins, just like I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.24,0:12:26.37,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,No one can erase it. No one can stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.68,0:12:29.87,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you my love.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.71,0:12:35.17,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll love you more deeply than anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.02,0:12:41.15,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll GIVE me your love?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.62,0:12:46.99,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's only natural for a princess to love a prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.86,0:12:51.09,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Love me more. Only me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.47,0:12:56.46,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Prince?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.54,0:13:00.34,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Not enough... Not enough love...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.08,0:13:04.57,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.15,0:13:11.42,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Lysander is someone in my grade from the sculpture\Ndivision, you see, and this is one of his works!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.42,0:13:12.92,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.92,0:13:15.52,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Your heart gets warm looking at it, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.52,0:13:17.43,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Uh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.43,0:13:21.70,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like it's filled with the feeling of love, somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.70,0:13:22.66,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.66,0:13:26.37,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,He must have been thinking about\Nsomebody while he created it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.37,0:13:28.20,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,But that might've been you, Hermia-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.20,0:13:31.64,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,No, definitely not! I know myself better\Nthan anyone else does, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.71,0:13:36.90,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that Lysander-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.51,0:13:38.57,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.91,0:13:40.68,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't he seem kind?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.68,0:13:42.67,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.86,0:13:48.82,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Meow...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.82,0:13:51.89,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the mime for "Do you mean me?"!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.89,0:13:54.36,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that mime supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.36,0:13:56.46,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,The mime for marriage!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.23,0:13:58.89,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.30,0:14:01.03,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,The mime for a vow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.50,0:14:02.94,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the mime for "no."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.94,0:14:03.84,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Meow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.04,0:14:08.87,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,That was close, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.28,0:14:13.92,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Won't you write a love letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.92,0:14:17.08,Notes,,0000,0000,0000,,Lovey-dovey, donkey-lonkey, love-dovey, donkey-lonkey...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.38,0:14:16.18,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Qua...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.18,0:14:17.39,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that sound, I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.08,0:14:20.32,Notes,,0000,0000,0000,,Lovey-dovey! Lovey-dovey, donkey-lonkey, lovey-dovey,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.39,0:14:21.29,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I, um, something important's come up! That is, well, goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.32,0:14:23.38,Notes,,0000,0000,0000,,donkey-lonkey, lovey-dovey, donkey-lonkey, lovey...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.16,0:14:28.56,Notes,,0000,0000,0000,,Lovey-dovey, donkey-lonkey, lovey-dovey, donkey-lonkey,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.56,0:14:31.13,Notes,,0000,0000,0000,,lovey-dovey, donkey-lonkey, lovey-dovey, donkey-lonkey...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.46,0:14:31.00,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.13,0:14:33.97,Notes,,0000,0000,0000,,Lovey-dovey, donkey-lonkey, lovey-dovey, donkey-lonkey...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.13,0:14:34.24,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Fakir!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.97,0:14:36.40,Notes,,0000,0000,0000,,Lovey-dovey, donkey-lonkey, lovey-dovey, donkey-lonkey,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.90,0:14:37.21,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing playing with Uzura?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.40,0:14:38.74,Notes,,0000,0000,0000,,Lovey-dovey, donkey-lonkey, lovey-dovey...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.54,0:14:39.74,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I keep telling you to be a little quieter!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.74,0:14:40.71,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.98,0:14:44.05,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Fakir, you're researching in books again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.05,0:14:47.18,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just doing what I can, even if it's only a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.18,0:14:48.72,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I've cast aside my sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.72,0:14:49.81,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.95,0:14:53.55,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Uzura-chan. We're in the way, so let's go, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.96,0:14:56.52,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to be a little quieter!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.96,0:14:57.53,Notes,,0000,0000,0000,,Lovey-dovey, donkey-lonkey, lovey-dovey, donkey-lonkey...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.52,0:14:57.53,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.53,0:14:59.33,Notes,,0000,0000,0000,,Lovey-dovey, donkey-lonkey, lovey-dovey, donkey-lonkey...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.33,0:15:03.16,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Why am I so obsessed with books?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.16,0:15:07.44,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,But no matter what book I open, they've\Nall had the endings torn out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.44,0:15:09.44,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,The ghost knight's book was the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.44,0:15:12.17,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,But I saw the end of that book in my dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.17,0:15:14.64,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! What does this mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.64,0:15:16.84,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to be quiet in the library, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.84,0:15:19.75,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,That under-developed Hermia, of all people!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.75,0:15:21.82,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe she's with Mytho-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.82,0:15:24.69,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this is so vexing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.89,0:15:24.69,Person2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.19,0:15:27.19,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.19,0:15:29.69,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen with Mytho and Hermia-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.69,0:15:30.93,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,"Something," she says!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.93,0:15:31.99,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,They're on a DATE!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.99,0:15:35.00,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,They were holding hands and going towards\Nthe grove behind the school!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.00,0:15:36.06,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,The grove behind the school...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.06,0:15:37.43,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's such a shock, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.43,0:15:38.90,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you dig with us too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.90,0:15:41.87,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, that's okay! Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.17,0:15:45.71,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hermia... No, Bottom the donkey-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.71,0:15:49.51,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,You knew I was Bottom the donkey?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.51,0:15:52.81,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only one I've been looking at all this time, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.81,0:15:54.68,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I know everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.68,0:15:56.65,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the fact that you like Lysander.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.65,0:15:58.95,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, here, these are today's letters!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.95,0:16:00.22,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,They don't matter anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.22,0:16:01.12,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.12,0:16:03.72,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,You are my princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.72,0:16:04.39,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.39,0:16:07.45,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're my prima and mine alone, Hermia.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.23,0:16:14.77,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,The reason you deliver other people's letters is so you can forget\Nthat you yourself don't have the courage to confess your own love.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.77,0:16:16.67,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.67,0:16:20.24,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,You make it look like it's goodwill, but it's all for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.24,0:16:21.61,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.61,0:16:22.48,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.48,0:16:23.95,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.95,0:16:24.91,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.91,0:16:27.95,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone else is using you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.95,0:16:31.85,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,So from now on, you can just think only about yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.85,0:16:35.22,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,If you love me, you won't have to fool yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.22,0:16:39.63,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Love only me, and regard all others with hatred.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.63,0:16:45.60,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'll love only you, and hate everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.60,0:16:52.87,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Then as proof, you'll give me your beautiful heart, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.87,0:16:53.93,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.58,0:16:57.24,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Then come into my arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.88,0:16:59.74,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me your heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.98,0:17:06.92,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,If I have you, I can become a prima ballerina, can't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.92,0:17:09.75,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I've had enough of being the go-between\Nfor other people's loves.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.16,0:17:14.33,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, I'll act for my own sake...For Mytho-sama's sake...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.33,0:17:18.59,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, sacrifice your life for my sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.60,0:17:20.76,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hermia-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.92,0:17:42.79,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hermia-san, don't go over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.73,0:17:46.96,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to interfere?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.83,0:17:51.50,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Dance with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.50,0:17:52.56,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,With you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.13,0:17:56.00,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hermia, hurry up and come over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.00,0:17:58.84,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me your love.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.84,0:18:00.81,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Mytho-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.18,0:18:07.20,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.62,0:18:09.95,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, come into my arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.95,0:18:15.89,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hermia-san, is that really okay? Is it okay to end your love?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.89,0:18:17.86,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Without ever having said anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.13,0:18:23.16,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine! You can just throw away a stupid love like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.16,0:18:26.76,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Love can just go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.07,0:18:30.57,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true. It's not stupid at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.57,0:18:33.44,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a precious feeling of yours, Hermia-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.44,0:18:35.88,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Being unable to say that one word is love.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.44,0:18:41.74,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,But if that's truly a precious feeling,\Nthrowing it away would be cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.32,0:18:47.65,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want you to hide that feeling behind\Nyour back, I want you to tell him about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.89,0:18:55.63,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,If... If I were allowed, I would also...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.63,0:18:57.15,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,If I were allowed...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.27,0:19:05.24,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Begone from inside me, Raven!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.64,0:19:11.68,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, I... I haven't told Lysander anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.68,0:19:13.91,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I've told nothing of my feelings...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.91,0:19:15.04,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.38,0:19:22.72,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,The feeling that's grown to the bursting\Npoint inside you, that's real love.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.72,0:19:26.76,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, what you're seeking is false love!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.76,0:19:28.32,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's counterfeit love!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.13,0:19:32.19,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! What is this "real love"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.77,0:19:37.50,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,If this love is false, then all the love\Nin this world is false love!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.54,0:19:44.03,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hermia-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.95,0:19:46.34,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Lysander...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.29,0:19:59.62,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I found Duck's lovey-dovey zura!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.77,0:20:08.70,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.37,0:20:19.81,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, um, Lysander, you might be surprised\Nat me saying this out of the blue, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.81,0:20:22.37,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.75,0:20:25.58,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Lysander, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.89,0:20:28.88,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.36,0:20:37.70,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Could that be...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.70,0:20:42.36,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I made you my model without asking you because, you see,\NI thought when I finished it I'd confess my love to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.38,0:20:50.04,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.04,0:20:50.78,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.78,0:20:52.61,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday, Uzura brought this to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.61,0:20:57.85,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't write it! Pike and Lilie wrote it! So, what should I say...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.25,0:20:59.24,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.16,0:21:03.85,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't waste time doing stupid stuff, idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.66,0:21:05.92,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.80,0:21:10.26,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,"Real love"? Don't make me laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.26,0:21:13.20,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone just wants to BE loved, that's all!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.20,0:21:15.14,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,My poor prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.14,0:21:19.64,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure Father's blood will save you from your suffering soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.64,0:21:22.81,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, we have to capture a sacrifice.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.81,0:21:25.34,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. For our own sakes too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.88,0:21:28.58,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.05,0:21:32.32,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just going to feed the foolish raven a meal, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.32,0:21:36.35,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,As a little token of my thanks for awakening me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.16,0:21:42.66,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, this was the story of the\Nprince and the raven, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.10,0:21:47.50,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, the fight began a long, long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.50,0:21:50.96,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't forgotten that, have you, Little Duck?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.00,0:23:28.77,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is this woman who can take the bite out of Fakir-sama?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.77,0:23:30.70,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,An older-woman lover has made her appearance, huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.70,0:23:34.58,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,The stories that boy wrote sometimes came true.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.58,0:23:37.68,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll protect Mytho as a knight. I won't take orders from you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.68,0:23:40.45,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,And it was starting to look like we'd\Nbe able to work together too...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.45,0:23:41.12,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.12,0:23:43.88,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Mytho! I won't allow you to hurt Raetsel!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.88,0:23:46.69,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! The two of you fighting is...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.69,0:23:48.86,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,You know you can't lay a finger on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.69,0:23:55.23,Notes,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Forgotten Story"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.86,0:23:52.26,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,All you children who love stories, come gather around.
